divs: sighting detailswhatever this was 5;45 am it was loud and sounded like a jet flying low\fast and sounded like it circled back for a sec which if it was landing at the airport it would change direction alittle to line up with the runway. it was startling to hear this in greeley. i have seen the fighter jets and this was big whatever it was. i think it was a jet by the engine sound but no lights? was higher than treetop but still i would say below cloud cover. it may bave been an 18 wheeler cause of our proximity to hwy 85. but the sound was different. i am puzzled by this.
